## Exercise 5: Summarizing Log Data

### Steps:

1. Requests per IP:

```bash
awk '{print $1}' access.log | sort | uniq -c | sort -nr
```

2. Requests per day:

```bash
awk '{print $4}' access.log | cut -d: -f1 | sort | uniq -c
```

3. Most requested URLs:

```bash
awk '{print $7}' access.log | sort | uniq -c | sort -nr
```

